cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.AI. 

The paper is about Online Learning to Rank (OLTR) for Information Retrieval, which is a subfield of Information Retrieval (IR) and Machine Learning (ML). Therefore, cs.IR and cs.LG are the most likely categories. The paper also discusses similarity-based ranking, which is related to Natural Language Processing (NLP) and Computer Vision (CV), hence cs.CL and cs.CV are also likely categories. Finally, the paper proposes a new model that balances speed and quality, which is a common problem in ML, so cs.AI is also a possible category.
